---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Partners" description="Official partners and suspension brands we work with - Penske, Nitron, Hyperco, Eibach, and AiM Sports.">
  
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="stripe-accent"></span>
      <h1>Our <span class="text-green">Partners</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">We work with the best names in motorsport suspension and data acquisition.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partners List -->
  <section class="partners-section">
    <div class="container">
      
      <!-- Penske -->
      <div class="partner-block">
        <div class="partner-header">
          <h2>Penske Racing Shocks</h2>
          <span class="partner-tagline">The Choice of Champions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="partner-content">
          <p>Penske Racing Shocks has been at the forefront of motorsport damper technology for over 50 years. From Formula 1 to NASCAR, IndyCar to Le Mans – Penske dampers have won at the highest levels of motorsport.</p>
          <p>We're proud to work with Penske dampers and offer their products to our customers. The Penske 7500 series is particularly well-suited to lightweight sports cars like Caterhams, offering the same technology used in professional racing in a package that fits the Seven platform.</p>
          <div class="partner-services">
            <h4>Our Penske Services:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Sales of Penske damper kits</li>
              <li>Custom valving and specification</li>
              <li>Service and rebuild</li>
              <li>Application development</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Nitron -->
      <div class="partner-block">
        <div class="partner-header">
          <h2>Nitron Racing Systems</h2>
          <span class="partner-tagline">British Engineering Excellence</span>
        </div>
        <div class="partner-content">
          <p>Nitron Racing Systems is a British manufacturer producing high-quality race and performance dampers. Their products are designed, developed, and manufactured in the UK – making them a natural fit for British sports car applications.</p>
          <p>The Nitron NTR range offers exceptional performance at competitive price points. We particularly recommend the NTR1 40mm – it's a robust, well-engineered damper that responds well to our custom valving.</p>
          <div class="partner-services">
            <h4>Our Nitron Services:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Full range of Nitron dampers</li>
              <li>Service and revalving</li>
              <li>Setup consultation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Hyperco -->
      <div class="partner-block">
        <div class="partner-header">
          <h2>Hyperco Springs</h2>
          <span class="partner-tagline">Precision Spring Technology</span>
        </div>
        <div class="partner-content">
          <p>Hyperco manufactures high-performance racing springs using advanced materials and manufacturing processes. Their springs maintain consistent rate under repeated compression cycles – essential for predictable handling.</p>
          <p>We spec Hyperco springs for applications where spring quality and consistency matter. For serious track use and racing, they're the benchmark for coilover springs.</p>
          <div class="partner-services">
            <h4>Our Hyperco Services:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Spring selection and specification</li>
              <li>Custom rate combinations</li>
              <li>Complete spring packages</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Eibach -->
      <div class="partner-block">
        <div class="partner-header">
          <h2>Eibach Springs</h2>
          <span class="partner-tagline">Performance Springs Since 1951</span>
        </div>
        <div class="partner-content">
          <p>Eibach has been manufacturing high-quality performance springs for over 70 years. From OEM supplier to motorsport specialist, their springs are trusted worldwide.</p>
          <p>We use Eibach springs as standard on many of our builds. They offer excellent quality, wide availability, and consistent performance – everything you need from a coilover spring.</p>
          <div class="partner-services">
            <h4>Our Eibach Services:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Spring supply and specification</li>
              <li>Rate selection for your application</li>
              <li>Helper spring packages</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- AiM -->
      <div class="partner-block">
        <div class="partner-header">
          <h2>AiM Sports</h2>
          <span class="partner-tagline">Data Acquisition & Displays</span>
        </div>
        <div class="partner-content">
          <p>AiM produces professional-grade data acquisition systems and displays. From club racing to professional motorsport, their products help drivers and engineers understand and improve performance.</p>
          <p>We use AiM equipment for our own development work and chassis setup services. Data logging lets us see exactly what's happening with the suspension – information that drives our setup decisions.</p>
          <div class="partner-services">
            <h4>Our AiM Services:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Data logging setup and support</li>
              <li>Suspension analysis using logged data</li>
              <li>Driver coaching and data review</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Partners Matter -->
  <section class="partners-why">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="why-content">
        <span class="stripe-accent"></span>
        <h2>Why Partnerships Matter</h2>
        <p>We've chosen to work with these brands because they represent the best in their respective fields. When you come to us for suspension work, you're getting components and expertise that's proven at the highest levels of motorsport.</p>
        <p>Our relationships with these manufacturers give us access to technical support, development resources, and the latest products. That knowledge flows directly into the work we do for you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Need Help Choosing?</h2>
        <p>Not sure which brand or product is right for you? Get in touch – we'll help you find the best solution for your application and budget.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Page Hero */
  .page-hero {
    padding: calc(80px + var(--space-xl)) 0 var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(92, 184, 92, 0.2);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* Partners Section */
  .partners-section {
    background: var(--tftr-black);
  }

  .partner-block {
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .partner-block:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .partner-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .partner-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .partner-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .partner-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .partner-content p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.8;
    grid-column: 1;
  }

  .partner-services {
    grid-column: 2;
    grid-row: 1 / 3;
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--tftr-green);
    align-self: start;
  }

  .partner-services h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .partner-services ul {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .partner-services li {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .partner-services li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
  }

  /* Why Partners Matter */
  .partners-why {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  .why-content {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .why-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .why-content p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--tftr-green-dark), var(--tftr-green));
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    color: var(--tftr-black);
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: var(--space-sm) auto var(--space-md);
    max-width: 50ch;
  }

  .cta-content .btn-primary {
    background: var(--tftr-black);
    color: var(--tftr-white);
  }

  .cta-content .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .partner-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .partner-content p {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: auto;
    }

    .partner-services {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
